{"tid":1622844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣手足 可唔可以爭氣啲","createTime":"2019-10-04T17:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T19:22:17.000Z","uid":36489,"like":24,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9eff7b3c00abbd9d805ad599829964029d0424e8","tid":1622844,"uid":36489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:24:08.000Z","msg":"我地話晒有警黑坊又有兩間狗屋<br />\n屌你老母竟然有人大叫前面係狗屋唔好再行？<br />\n大佬呀 10 月喇<br />\n用左緊急法喇 <br />\n日日用實彈嫁<br />\n<br />\n屌10點幾大叫留力聽日<br />\n成晚都無狗<br />\n見嗰幾架狗車老撚咁遠行過就驚<br />\n得嗰一排 green objects 就動物大遷徙咁走<br />\n大佬叫左成晚咩香港人反抗<br />\n我第一次見遮陣都無就散撚晒<br />\n<br />\n唉對唔住無意分化但真係好撚嬲呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n我地示威呀 唔撚係示弱呀</span><br />\n<br />\n我好愛你地嫁 但可唔可以爭氣啲<br />\n我地無下次嫁"},{"pid":"7005baa96ec96a7e0c04f9643b49c73dde4f68dd","tid":1622844,"uid":36489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"DLLM 1"},{"pid":"80cf9e167e5eb21eae29e75bfe5ceb0cea1bfff5","tid":1622844,"uid":107596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"重陣地？"},{"pid":"7421b560bb64f432450c962a54e63feaf418c220","tid":1622844,"uid":173814,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:30:15.000Z","msg":"荃灣拆左黨鐵同中銀，讀左宣言，已經無目標可以做野。不戀戰不被捕不流血，做哂，仲想點？"},{"pid":"993f5f3022b0d0e1daedfa2a2d838c7977b5c266","tid":1622844,"uid":153160,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:30:19.000Z","msg":"出過咁多次荃灣就知肯打既唔多<br />\n聽得最多次既係比人包抄<br />\n呢兩日仲要啲狗都唔理我地"},{"pid":"b038f51f278f54a75468e5adfb819ba1bd3b5d75","tid":1622844,"uid":152584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"目標做晒 唔走做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5a50cf6e3f4e2343d831db682136b21883c6b9","tid":1622844,"uid":36489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b038f51f278f54a75468e5adfb819ba1bd3b5d75","tid":1622844,"uid":152584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"